# GameNative — Design System & Layouts

## Part 1 — Color Tokens

Write all of these into `app/src/main/res/values/colors.xml`.
Replace ALL existing color references. Do not keep any default Material purple or gray values.

### Background tier
```
gn_bg_deepest   = #09090F   — main window background (near-black)
gn_bg_surface   = #12121C   — cards, bottom sheets
gn_bg_elevated  = #1A1A28   — elevated panels, search bars
gn_bg_overlay   = #22223A   — hover / selected / pressed states
```

### Accent (Steam blue)
```
gn_accent_primary = #1E9FFF  — CTAs, links, active nav icon
gn_accent_glow    = #3DB8FF  — glow ring, shimmer highlight
gn_accent_dim     = #1066A8  — pressed state of primary
gn_accent_subtle  = #1E9FFF26  — 15% alpha, used for ripple and selected backgrounds
```

### Neon pops — use SPARINGLY, badges and status indicators only
```
gn_neon_teal   = #00E5C3  — "Installed" badge
gn_neon_purple = #7C6EFA  — achievements, XP bar fill
gn_neon_orange = #FF7B54  — warnings, sale price tags
```

### Typography
```
gn_text_primary   = #EEEEF5  — all readable body text
gn_text_secondary = #8A8AA8  — subtitles, metadata, timestamps
gn_text_tertiary  = #505068  — disabled, placeholder
gn_text_on_accent = #FFFFFF  — text sitting on colored buttons or chips
```

### Status colors
```
gn_status_installed   = #00E5C3
gn_status_downloading = #1E9FFF
gn_status_error       = #FF4D6A
gn_status_not_installed — do NOT define a color; hide the chip entirely
                          (chip.visibility = GONE) when state is NOT_INSTALLED
```

### Structure
```
gn_divider     = #FFFFFF0F  — 6% white, hairline separators
gn_border_card = #FFFFFF18  — 9% white, card outline stroke
gn_scrim_art   = #A0000000  — 63% black overlay on hero art
```

### Legacy aliases — keep so existing references still compile
```xml
<color name="colorPrimary">@color/gn_accent_primary</color>
<color name="colorPrimaryDark">@color/gn_bg_deepest</color>
<color name="colorAccent">@color/gn_accent_glow</color>
<color name="windowBackground">@color/gn_bg_deepest</color>
```

