## Part 2 — Typography (Outfit from Google Fonts)

Add these font files to `app/src/main/res/font/`:
```
outfit_regular.ttf    weight 400
outfit_medium.ttf     weight 500
outfit_semibold.ttf   weight 600
outfit_bold.ttf       weight 700
```

Create matching XML font descriptors in `res/font/` using Android's font resource
file format so they are accessible as `@font/outfit_*`.

Define these `TextAppearance` styles in `themes.xml`:

| Style name | Font | Size | Color |
|---|---|---|---|
| `TextAppearance.GameNative.GameTitle` | outfit_semibold | 15sp | gn_text_primary |
| `TextAppearance.GameNative.GameMeta` | outfit_regular | 12sp | gn_text_secondary |
| `TextAppearance.GameNative.SectionHeader` | outfit_medium | 11sp | gn_text_tertiary, ALL_CAPS, letterSpacing=0.10 |

