## Part 4 — Layout: fragment_app_list.xml (Library screen)

File: `app/src/main/res/layout/fragment_app_list.xml`
This is the main game library screen. Map to the existing screen/fragment
that lists the user's Steam games (e.g. `LibraryScreen`, `LibraryListPane`,
or `AppListFragment` — use whatever name already exists in the codebase).

Root: `CoordinatorLayout`, `fitsSystemWindows=true`, background=gn_bg_deepest

```
CoordinatorLayout
│
├── AppBarLayout (elevation=0dp, liftOnScroll=true, target=recyclerViewGames)
│   │
│   ├── ConstraintLayout (paddingH=16dp, paddingTop=8dp)
│   │   ├── TextView  "GameNative"  (26sp, outfit_bold, top-left)
│   │   ├── ImageButton  sort icon  (36dp pill bg, top-right)
│   │   ├── ImageButton  grid/list toggle  (36dp pill bg, left of sort)
│   │   └── SearchBar  (height=52dp, full width, below title)
│   │
│   └── HorizontalScrollView (no scrollbar, paddingH=12dp, paddingBottom=10dp)
│       └── ChipGroup (singleSelection=true, selectionRequired=true)
│           Chips: "All" (pre-checked), "Installed", "Recent",
│                  "Favorites", "Not Installed"
│
├── RecyclerView  id=recyclerViewGames
│   paddingStart/End=10dp, paddingBottom=80dp (clears bottom nav height)
│   clipToPadding=false, scrollbars=none
│   layout_behavior = appbar_scrolling_view_behavior
│
├── LinearLayout  id=layoutEmptyState  (visibility=gone, gravity=center)
│   96dp icon + title text + subtitle text
│
└── ShimmerFrameLayout  id=shimmerLayout  (visibility=gone)
    shimmer_base_color=gn_bg_elevated
    shimmer_highlight_color=gn_bg_overlay
    shimmer_auto_start=true
```

