## Part 5 — Layout: item_app_grid.xml (Game card)

File: `app/src/main/res/layout/item_app_grid.xml`
Used as the RecyclerView grid item.

Root: `MaterialCardView` (cornerRadius=12dp, elevation=0dp, strokeColor=gn_border_card)

```
MaterialCardView
└── ConstraintLayout
    │
    ├── ImageView  id=imgGameCover
    │   width=0dp height=0dp scaleType=centerCrop
    │   app:layout_constraintDimensionRatio="2:3"   ← CRITICAL — portrait capsule art
    │   constrained start / end / top of parent
    │
    ├── View  id=scrimGradient  (drawable: gradient_card_scrim)
    │   height=100dp, pinned to BOTTOM of imgGameCover
    │
    ├── TextView  id=tvGameTitle
    │   anchored to bottom-left of cover, rightMargin clears btnFavorite
    │   textAppearance=GameTitle, maxLines=2, ellipsize=end
    │
    ├── ImageButton  id=btnFavorite
    │   32dp, background=bg_icon_pill, pinned top-right corner of cover
    │   src: ic_heart_outline or ic_heart_filled depending on state
    │
    ├── Chip  id=chipStatus
    │   anchored bottom-right of cover, height=24dp, cornerRadius=12dp
    │   Color driven by InstallState — see adapter spec
    │
    ├── LinearProgressIndicator  id=progressDownload
    │   height=3dp, visibility=GONE by default
    │   indicatorColor=gn_accent_primary, trackColor=gn_bg_overlay
    │   Shown only when installState == DOWNLOADING
    │
    └── TextView  id=tvGameMeta
        Below the cover art, 8dp padding
        textAppearance=GameMeta, single line, ellipsize=end
        content: "12.4 GB  •  2.3 hrs"
```

