## Part 6 — Layout: item_app_list.xml (List view alternate)

File: `app/src/main/res/layout/item_app_list.xml`
Used when user switches to list view mode.

Root: `MaterialCardView` — horizontal orientation

```
MaterialCardView (horizontal)
├── ImageView  80×80dp  (Coil RoundedCornersTransformation(8f))
│   src: iconImageUrl  (Steam 32×32 icon, NOT the 600×900 capsule)
│
└── ConstraintLayout (flex)
    ├── TextView  id=tvGameTitle  (15sp, outfit_semibold)
    ├── TextView  id=tvGameMeta   (12sp, gn_text_secondary)
    ├── Chip  id=chipStatus       (same logic as grid card)
    └── LinearProgressIndicator  id=progressDownload  (same as grid card)
```

